# GreenTech Storyblok Astro Project

This is an Astro project that uses Storyblok as a headless CMS. The project is set up with Tailwind CSS for styling and React for interactive components.

## Key Files

- Main configuration: [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs)
- Package dependencies: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- TypeScript configuration: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Environment variables: [.env](mdc:.env)

## Build and Development

The project can be run in different environments:
- Development: `npm run dev` (runs with preview token)
- Production build: `npm run build:production`
- Preview build: `npm run build:preview`

## Deployment

The project includes Docker configurations for both static and SSR deployments:
- Static deployment: [Dockerfile.static](mdc:Dockerfile.static)
- SSR deployment: [Dockerfile.ssr](mdc:Dockerfile.ssr)
- Nginx configuration: [nginx/](mdc:nginx)
